(a + b)\%n = (a\%n + b\%n)\%n.
(4^{30}-2^{50}) \mod 5 = (1-4) \mod 5 = 2
4^{30}\equiv 1
2^{50}\equiv 4
4^{30}-2^{50}\equiv 1-4\equiv2.
